parameters:
Clea: Is this Yuan's hideout...? What kind of demon is
Yuan?

Mage Relm: Yuan is one of the seven demons who were
defeated by the hero. He is feared as the demon of gluttony
and is often used as an 'example' of a long cave.
Mage Relm: This is a troublesome place for us, isn't it?
Priestess Sophia: Nora-chan... Are you okay?

Thief Nora: Um, c-can't we turn back? Isn't it enough to
just tell the general about this place and be done with
it...?

Clea: We still don't know if there are ogres here, and if
we're going to fight dragons, we can't back down from
ogres.

Mage Relm: That's right! We can't run away from just
ogres!

Priestess Sophia: I agree with Nora-chan, but should we
confirm if there are ogres here first?

Thief Nora: I-I understand... But there is definitely
something here... I can smell it.

Thief Nora: A smell I've never encountered before... It's
the scent of violence and strong blood... Ugh...
Mage Relm: Haa...haa...I thought I was going to die...!

Mage Relm: Clea-san, what's wrong!? If you're feeling
unwell, please let us know in advance!

Thief Nora: Eeek!? P-Please calm down, everything is
alright now!

Clea: Everyone will be killed by that person...! We need to
escape quickly, or else Father and Mother will end up the
same way...

Clea: W-We humans can't stand a chance against... That
person, they're not someone to be taken lightly...!

Clea: I can't die... because I was entrusted with it... to
Father...!
Thief Nora: Where are we going to escape to?

Thief Nora: Clea-san has her hometown village, Relm-san has
the academy, and Sophia-san has the church...

Thief Nora: But I don't have a place to escape to. I don't
know my hometown or the location of the Emma Thief Guild
right now.

Thief Nora: If you're going to escape, please escape on
your own. I can't even escape without defeating the dragon.

Thief Nora: I will go. I will defeat the ogre to defeat the
dragon.

Thief Nora: As Clea-san taught me, I will never give up. I
will fight until the end.
Priestess Sophia: Nora-chan, have you calmed down?
Thief Nora: Ugh... I-I said something terrible...

Priestess Sophia: How about taking a rest until tomorrow
morning? I think it's necessary for everyone to sort out
their thoughts.

Thief Nora: Clea-san isn't coming... ugh... it's my
fault...

Priestess Sophia: Clea-chan had doubts... There must have
been something I unintentionally didn't consider.

Priestess Sophia: That's why it was supposed to turn out
like this... Since Clea-chan isn't coming, should we rely on
General Atu?
Mage Relm: Um... Can we wait just a little longer?

Priestess Sophia: This is already the third time. We also
need to think about the future...

Priestess Sophia: If possible, I wanted to continue the
adventure with Clea-chan until the end.

Clea: I became an adventurer to pursue the dragon and
avenge my parents...!

Clea: I've always thought that I was chasing after the
dragon for the sake of my parents.

Clea: But it's not just that... I came here for myself, for
my own satisfaction!

Clea: To take a new step forward! It's to walk my own life,
satisfied with myself.

Clea: For me, living happily means forgetting everything...
There is absolutely no way to live by just existing!

Clea: So please, let me ask again... Please let me join
everyone on this journey to defeat the dragon!

Thief Nora: Yes... of course! Ugh... I'm glad... I'm sorry
for saying something mean!

Mage Relm: It can't be helped! Let's forgive her this time
with a generous heart!

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, you're not very obedient, are you?
Nice to meet you again, Clea-chan.

Clea: Thank you very much... I won't run away anymore,
let's challenge the Ogre.
